你能够调用以下的API:
[['MarketResearch.get_demand_report', {'name': 'MarketResearch.get_demand_report', 'description': 'This function retrieves the demand report for a specific industry in a given location.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'industry', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The industry for which the demand report is required.'}, {'name': 'location', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The location where the demand is being analyzed.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'report', 'description': 'A detailed demand report for the specified industry and location.'}]}], ['MedicalInstitution.assess_technical_level', {'name': 'MedicalInstitution.assess_technical_level', 'description': 'This function assesses the technical level of a medical institution given its ID.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'institutionId', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The ID of the medical institution.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'technicalLevel', 'description': 'An assessment of the institution’s technical capabilities.'}]}], ['MedicalInstitution.get_talent_team', {'name': 'MedicalInstitution.get_talent_team', 'description': 'This function retrieves information about the talent team of a medical institution given its ID.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'institutionId', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The ID of the medical institution.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'teamInfo', 'description': 'Information about the institution’s talent team.'}]}], ['InstitutionImpact.predict_social_influence', {'name': 'InstitutionImpact.predict_social_influence', 'description': 'This function predicts the social influence of multiple institutions based on their IDs.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'institutionIds', 'type': 'ARRAY', 'description': 'An array of institution IDs to predict social influence for.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'influencePrediction', 'description': 'A prediction of the social influence for the selected institutions.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `MarketResearch.get_demand_report` 并传入 `industry` 和 `location`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "MarketResearch.get_demand_report",
    "args": "{'industry': 'medical', 'location': 'China'}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
